    <title>ITerm2</title>
    <link href="https://xubin.github.io/2016/02/10/ITerm2/"/>
    <id>https://xubin.github.io/2016/02/10/ITerm2/</id>
    <published>2016-02-10T04:55:51.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-12-15T05:16:44.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="MAC-iTerm-2-配置"><a href="#MAC-iTerm-2-配置" class="headerlink" title="MAC iTerm 2 配置"></a>MAC iTerm 2 配置</h1><h2 id="下载-iTerm-2"><a href="#下载-iTerm-2" class="headerlink" title="下载 iTerm 2"></a>下载 iTerm 2</h2><p><a href="http://www.iterm2.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">iTerm 2</a></p><h2 id="下载字体库"><a href="#下载字体库" class="headerlink" title="下载字体库"></a>下载字体库</h2><hr><p><a href="https://github.com/seebi/dircolors-solarized" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github</a><br><a href="https://github.com/altercation/solarized" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/altercation/solarized</a><br><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone git://github.com/seebi/dircolors-solarized.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="Vim-配置"><a href="#Vim-配置" class="headerlink" title="Vim 配置"></a>Vim 配置</h2><hr><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span> mkdir ~/.vim/colors</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span> cp solarized/vim-colors-solarized/colors/solarized.vim  ~/.vim/colors/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span> vi ~/.vimrc</span><br><span class="line">syntax enable</span><br><span class="line">set background=dark</span><br><span class="line">colorscheme solarized</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="ls"><a href="#ls" class="headerlink" title="ls"></a>ls</h2><hr><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span> vi ~/.bash_profile</span><br><span class="line">export CLICOLOR=1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="iTerm-2-DIY"><a href="#iTerm-2-DIY" class="headerlink" title="iTerm 2  DIY"></a>iTerm 2  DIY</h2><hr><ul><li><p>下载 <a href="https://developer.apple.com/download/more/?name=for%20Xcode%20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Command line</a>版本要和xcode对应 -不需要</p></li><li><p>下载iTerm2<a href="http://www.iterm2.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">下载</a></p></li><li>打开iTerm2 </li><li><blockquote><p>输入下面指令安装oh-my-zsh</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -L https://raw.github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/master/tools/install.sh | sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote></li></ul><ul><li><blockquote><p>卸载oh my zsh</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span> uninstall_oh_my_zsh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote></li><li><p>安装Powerline 如果出错需要 –user</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span> sudo easy_install pip</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span> pip install powerline-status --user</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="下载字体库下载powerline-fonts"><a href="#下载字体库下载powerline-fonts" class="headerlink" title="下载字体库下载powerline-fonts"></a>下载字体库<a href="https://github.com/powerline/fonts" target="_blank" rel="noopener">下载powerline-fonts</a></h2><hr><ul><li><p>安装字体库</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span> cd fonts-master</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span> ./install.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>安装完成后提示所有字体均已下载到/Users/用户名/Library/Fonts路径下</p></blockquote></li><li><p>设置iTerm 2的Regular Font 和 Non-ASCII Fonts</p><blockquote><p>安装完字体库之后，把iTerm 2的设置里的Profile中的Text 选项卡中里的Regular Font和Non-ASCII Font的字体都设置成 Powerline的字体，我这里设置的字体是12pt Meslo LG S DZ Regular for Powerline</p></blockquote></li></ul><blockquote><p>如下图</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://github.com/xubin/xubin.github.io/blob/master/res/iTerm2/iTerm2_3.png?raw=true" alt="图1"><br><img src="https://github.com/xubin/xubin.github.io/blob/master/res/iTerm2/iTerm2_1.png?raw=true" alt="图1"><br><img src="https://github.com/xubin/xubin.github.io/blob/master/res/iTerm2/iTerm2_2.png?raw=true" alt="图1"></p><h2 id="配色方案下载"><a href="#配色方案下载" class="headerlink" title="配色方案下载"></a>配色方案<a href="https://github.com/altercation/solarized" target="_blank" rel="noopener">下载</a></h2><hr><ul><li>solarized/iterm2-colors-solarized 下双击 Solarized Dark.itermcolors 和 Solarized Light.itermcolors 两个文件就可以把配置文件导入到 iTerm2 里</li><li>通过load presets选择刚刚安装的配色主题即可<h2 id="安装agnoster"><a href="#安装agnoster" class="headerlink" title="安装agnoster"></a>安装agnoster</h2></li></ul><hr><ul><li>到下载的工程里面运行install文件,主题将安装到~/.oh-my-zsh/themes目录下</li><li>设置该主题<br>编辑~／.zshrc 文件将ZSH_THEME=”agnoster”（agnoster即为要设置的主题）<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span> vim ~/.zshrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="指令效果zsh-syntax-highlighting下载"><a href="#指令效果zsh-syntax-highlighting下载" class="headerlink" title="指令效果zsh-syntax-highlighting下载"></a>指令效果<a href="https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting" target="_blank" rel="noopener">zsh-syntax-highlighting下载</a></h2><hr><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span> cd ~/.oh-my-zsh/custom/plugins/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span> git clone git://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting.git</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span> 修改 ~/.zshrc  plugins=(zsh-syntax-highlighting)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="自动命令提示"><a href="#自动命令提示" class="headerlink" title="自动命令提示"></a>自动命令提示</h2><hr><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span> cd ~/.oh-my-zsh/custom/plugins/</span><br><span class="line">git clone git://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span> vim ~/.zshrc </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span> plugins=(zsh-autosuggestions)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span> cd ~/.oh-my-zsh/custom/plugins/zsh-autosuggestions</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span>用 vim 打开 zsh-autosuggestions.zsh 文件，修改 ZSH_AUTOSUGGEST_HIGHLIGHT_STYLE='fg=10'</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="恢复默认命令"><a href="#恢复默认命令" class="headerlink" title="恢复默认命令"></a>恢复默认命令</h2><hr><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span>iTerm2 恢复默认设置</span><br><span class="line">defaults delete com.googlecode.iterm2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span>启动iTerm 2 默认使用dash改用zsh解决方法：</span><br><span class="line">chsh -s /bin/zsh</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span>如果想切换回原来的dash：</span><br><span class="line">chsh -s /bin/bash</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span>卸载oh my zsh，在命令行输入如下命令，回车即可：</span><br><span class="line">uninstall_oh_my_zsh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
